rows.label: qst006103_msg0002
rows.name:
Rex, isn't there
something written on it?

rows.label: qst006103_msg0005
rows.name:
The name of the kingdom
is... Rigideria.

rows.label: qst006103_msg0006
rows.name:
It exists on a phantom Divine
Beast that moves freely and is
never seen by human eyes...

rows.label: qst006103_msg0007
rows.name:
However, in this place, it sank
overnight along with its people...

rows.label: qst006103_msg0010
rows.name:
If it sank, then there's
nothing more we can do...

rows.label: qst006103_msg0011
rows.name:
Hmph, what are you saying?
It is too early to give up!

rows.label: qst006103_msg0012
rows.name:
We know where the kingdom
sank. Then we should just
salvage its relics.

rows.label: qst006103_msg0013
rows.name:
That's impossible. How long
ago do you think that was?

rows.label: qst006103_msg0014
rows.name:
Relics of a phantom kingdom?
Nice... I'm getting excited!

rows.label: qst006103_msg0015
rows.name: What?! You're getting into it too, Rex?

rows.label: qst006103_msg0016
rows.name: Come, do not dawdle! Act at once!
